Control	Type	Purpose
REC	          Momentary pushbutton	Hold to record, release to play
MODE	        Toggle switch	Forward / Reverse
LOOP	        Toggle switch	One-shot / Loop
KILL	        Momentary pushbutton	Stop playback immediately
LED	          Indicator	Playback active

Pinout:
#define REC_PIN   2
#define MODE_PIN  3
#define LOOP_PIN  4
#define KILL_PIN  5
#define LED_PIN   13
